We are a forward-thinking technology company based in London, dedicated to delivering innovative software solutions that empower businesses. Our commitment to fostering a collaborative and inclusive work environment ensures that creativity and technical expertise thrive among our team members.', 'http://localhost:8000/jobs/cb0c2879-8c68-43e2-9ea6-28d4a9418256', 'posted', '2026-05-15 13:50:05.185636+00');
