INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('3c442deb-03f6-4b58-a8a1-231175057cb7', 'Senior Python Engineer', 'General', '**Job Title:** Senior Python Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a dynamic Series B fintech startup dedicated to transforming the financial landscape through innovative technology solutions. Our mission is to provide seamless and accessible financial services that empower individuals and businesses alike. Join us as we continue to grow and make a significant impact in the fintech industry.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a talented and experienced Senior Python Engineer to join our growing team in London. In this role, you will be responsible for designing, developing, and maintaining robust and scalable applications using Python. You will collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions that meet our business needs.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design and implement high-performance APIs using FastAPI.
- Develop and manage database systems with PostgreSQL.
- Collaborate with product managers, designers, and other engineers to define and deliver new features.
- Ensure code quality through rigorous testing and code reviews.
- Troubleshoot and debug applications to optimize performance.
- Stay updated with industry trends and emerging technologies to enhance our development practices.
- Contribute to architectural discussions and decision-making processes.
- Mentor junior engineers and share knowledge across the team.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proficiency in Python programming, with a strong focus on FastAPI.
- Experience with PostgreSQL and database design.
- Solid understanding of software development principles and best practices.
- Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
- Excellent communication and teamwork abilities.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Familiarity with containerization technologies, particularly Docker.
- Experience in the fintech sector or related industries.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary in the range of £70,000–£90,000, depending on experience.
- Opportunity to work in a fast-paced and innovative environment.
- Flexible work arrangements to support work-life balance.
- Professional development opportunities and career growth.
- A collaborative and inclusive company culture.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with flexible work arrangements available to accommodate individual needs. 

Join us in shaping the future of fintech! We look forward to receiving your application.', '[-0.010299683,-0.01637268,0.045898438,0.021316528,0.012649536,-0.0026760101,-0.029464722,0.080566406,0.0030498505,0.012802124,-0.009178162,-0.07562256,-0.03314209,-0.025100708,0.038757324,0.028121948,-0.055786133,0.00969696,-0.0256958,0.0068092346,0.036224365,-0.008369446,-0.003955841,0.014762878,0.015640259,-0.02909851,-0.026351929,0.01826477,-0.015686035,-0.023162842,0.041046143,-0.01852417,-0.061706543,0.08703613,-0.011505127,-0.013053894,0.026855469,0.07055664,0.017242432,7.2836876e-05,-0.010765076,-0.042785645,0.027191162,0.025314331,-0.0138549805,0.030853271,-0.024398804,0.002937317,0.014282227,-0.0033626556,-0.008728027,-0.009590149,-0.0064964294,0.02822876,-0.003660202,0.0038108826,-0.008857727,0.023284912,0.008575439,0.0034389496,0.03488159,-0.0041542053,0.035369873,0.004852295,-0.033081055,-0.0020771027,-0.035064697,0.046173096,-0.027130127,-0.009689331,0.04019165,0.039611816,-0.0051498413,-0.0060539246,0.049346924,-0.08288574,-0.029144287,0.055023193,-0.027038574,-0.046081543,-0.08660889,-0.03363037,0.028762817,-0.008605957,-0.013130188,-0.04611206,-0.012420654,-0.046569824,-0.016693115,0.034057617,-0.04675293,0.06335449,-0.002664566,0.05279541,0.0022411346,0.006340027,0.017654419,0.004016876,-0.041290283,0.024505615,0.03189087,0.015899658,0.021972656,0.0079422,0.048217773,0.0028953552,0.0055389404,-0.019256592,0.038330078,0.014930725,-0.06500244,0.013038635,-0.00040364265,-0.014717102,-0.043823242,-0.035858154,-0.054626465,-0.021331787,-0.011428833,-0.055145264,-0.015449524,-0.050354004,-0.013175964,-0.02281189,-0.023788452,0.004585266,-0.005130768,-0.0059280396,-0.027786255,-0.03253174,-0.014945984,-0.024871826,0.03451538,0.0067710876,0.011306763,-0.0234375,-0.06945801,0.026977539,-0.024780273,-0.022613525,-0.013824463,-0.0015163422,0.005340576,0.008544922,-0.06210327,0.0030555725,-0.028121948,0.013397217,-0.031585693,-0.0029182434,0.019378662,0.0385437,-0.062561