INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('4aba5bc3-0259-4d1b-9c5d-fdea86aa8ac8', 'Machine Learning Research Engineer', 'Research', '**Job Title:** Machine Learning Research Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are an industry-leading machine-learning software company based in Cambridge, dedicated to pushing the boundaries of AI applications. Our team is comprised of innovative researchers and engineers who are passionate about developing cutting-edge solutions that transform industries and improve lives.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a Machine Learning Research Engineer to join our dynamic research department. In this role, you will contribute to the development of advanced machine learning models and algorithms, collaborating with a team of experts to drive innovation and enhance our product offerings.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Conduct research to develop and improve machine learning algorithms and models.  
- Implement and evaluate machine learning solutions using Python frameworks such as PyTorch and TensorFlow.  
- Collaborate with cross-functional teams to integrate machine learning capabilities into existing products.  
- Analyze and interpret complex data sets to inform research and development efforts.  
- Stay up-to-date with the latest advancements in machine learning and AI technologies.  
- Present research findings and technical concepts to both technical and non-technical audiences.  
- Contribute to the publication of research papers and reports in relevant journals and conferences.  
- Mentor junior researchers and contribute to a collaborative team environment.  

**Required Skills:**  
- Ph.D. in a relevant field (e.g., Computer Science, Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence).  
- Strong understanding of traditional machine learning concepts and methodologies.  
- Proven experience in Python frameworks, specifically PyTorch and TensorFlow.  

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with deep learning techniques and architectures.  
- Familiarity with cloud computing platforms and deployment of machine learning models.  
- Knowledge of data engineering and data preprocessing techniques.  
- Experience in contributing to open-source projects or research collaborations.  

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of GBP 36,000 - 60,000 per year, commensurate with experience.  
- Opportunities for professional development and continuous learning.  
- A collaborative and inclusive work environment that values diversity.  
- Flexible working arrangements to support work-life balance.  

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in Cambridge, with options for flexible working arrangements to accommodate individual needs.  

We welcome applications from all individuals, regardless of background or identity, and look forward to hearing from you!', '[0.012008667,-0.00233078,0.047698975,0.008224487,0.010444641,0.007133484,-0.015655518,0.076049805,-0.028747559,0.0129852295,-0.015586853,-0.050445557,-0.00642395,0.0068969727,0.07196045,0.04336548,-0.050476074,0.019699097,-0.00409317,0.03048706,0.0046081543,0.010070801,0.010147095,0.00064992905,0.0029888153,-0.03262329,-0.00932312,0.018661499,-0.0005559921,-0.027648926,0.02293396,-0.0054244995,-0.08459473,0.02696228,-0.033203125,0.028198242,-0.012229919,0.03086853,-0.037750244,0.0028514862,-0.0093307495,-0.061798096,0.04547119,0.0513916,-0.056915283,-0.0041160583,-0.043395996,-0.03111267,0.014320374,0.009246826,-0.007850647,-0.027435303,-0.010139465,0.01272583,-0.0048599243,0.021911621,0.024765015,-0.001452446,0.0047912598,-0.00459671,0.025543213,-0.004787445,0.03967285,0.002166748,0.0021343231,-0.014770508,-0.035736084,0.039916992,-0.024795532,-0.005317688,0.050628662,0.0037555695,-0.027893066,-0.0023117065,0.03878784,-0.05923462,-0.02947998,0.049346924,-0.07098389,-0.011947632,-0.061309814,-0.00655365,0.03781128,-0.012184143,-0.027694702,-0.04559326,-0.0065994263,-0.066101074,-0.046875,0.014480591,-0.038970947,0.011489868,-0.019897461,0.038970947,0.02822876,0.0004003048,0.018447876,-0.008407593,-0.021957397,0.04397583,-0.024490356,-0.03665161,0.025878906,-0.021896362,0.039123535,0.009140015,0.012245178,-0.03564453,0.036895752,0.04425049,-0.06640625,0.02822876,0.0037822723,0.009506226,-0.046142578,-0.046173096,-0.024917603,-0.00028443336,-0.021911621,-0.050964355,-0.0524292,-0.02293396,0.024719238,-0.025283813,-0.008239746,0.023803711,0.01826477,-0.018066406,-0.010025024,-0.030181885,-0.00027132034,0.0039405823,0.0028438568,-0.009399414,0.016571045,-0.03173828,-0.027282715,0.018539429,-0.06512451,-0.04244995,0.010932922,-0.010978699,-0.046783447,0.050476074,-0.043823242,0.014984131,0.0051002502,0.02696228,-0.014770508,0.014221191,-0.001358985