INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('dee034e5-48cf-4077-8559-62924b9e4188', 'Staff NLP Engineer', 'AI Systems', '**Job Title:** Staff NLP Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are an AI-first technology platform dedicated to transforming the landscape of complex intellectual property research. By leveraging Natural Language Processing (NLP), Large Language Models (LLMs), and advanced search systems, we aim to provide innovative solutions that enhance research efficiency and accuracy.

**The Role:**  
As a Staff NLP Engineer, you will play a pivotal role in developing and implementing cutting-edge NLP solutions that drive our technology forward. You will collaborate with cross-functional teams to build robust production systems that handle large datasets and deliver impactful results.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design and develop scalable NLP systems for production use.  
- Collaborate with data scientists and engineers to integrate NLP solutions into existing workflows.  
- Build and maintain machine learning models using TensorFlow or PyTorch.  
- Implement and optimize search technologies such as Elasticsearch or OpenSearch.  
- Work with large datasets to train and evaluate language models.  
- Conduct research and stay updated on the latest advancements in NLP and machine learning.  
- Troubleshoot and resolve issues in production NLP systems.  
- Document processes and maintain clear communication with team members.  
- Mentor junior engineers and contribute to team knowledge sharing.  

**Required Skills:**  
- Strong experience in Python programming.  
- Proven commercial experience in Natural Language Processing (NLP).  
- Demonstrated experience in building production ML/NLP systems.  
- Proficiency with TensorFlow or PyTorch frameworks.  
- Familiarity with search technologies such as Elasticsearch or OpenSearch.  
- Experience working with large datasets or language systems.  

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with Large Language Models (LLMs) or information retrieval systems.  

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £90,000 – £110,000.  
- Equity options as part of the compensation package.  
- Opportunities for professional development and growth.  
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.  

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London with a hybrid work arrangement, requiring 2 days onsite per week.  

We are committed to creating a diverse and inclusive workplace. We welcome applications from all qualified individuals regardless of background or identity.', '[-0.020248413,0.025222778,0.0435791,0.0001487732,0.02558899,-0.0050621033,-0.035339355,0.06573486,-0.047607422,0.011146545,0.0020885468,-0.018157959,-0.013702393,4.708767e-06,0.040740967,0.037078857,-0.038330078,0.008995056,-0.032470703,0.03970337,0.022888184,0.014472961,-0.007457733,0.021850586,0.020507812,-0.029541016,-0.010032654,0.030792236,0.0053710938,-0.0039749146,0.005344391,-0.014389038,-0.06732178,0.07043457,-0.020370483,0.0025310516,0.02394104,0.040527344,-0.011993408,0.0036182404,-0.017837524,-0.039520264,0.026626587,0.018692017,-0.059814453,0.029434204,-0.053588867,0.016189575,0.016494751,0.0040893555,0.0017404556,-0.03643799,-0.0034866333,0.017242432,-0.009979248,0.0015506744,0.019500732,0.00447464,0.010368347,-0.027618408,0.0256958,-0.02720642,0.059326172,0.029052734,-0.013801575,-0.007217407,-0.021652222,0.008293152,-0.028747559,0.005710602,0.057647705,0.054229736,-0.0340271,-0.00349617,0.030593872,-0.0501709,-0.052368164,0.04650879,-0.037628174,-0.050445557,-0.06604004,0.016799927,0.01134491,-0.025756836,-0.016235352,-0.054229736,-0.020874023,-0.041931152,-0.062072754,0.008293152,-0.037078857,0.011909485,-0.023223877,0.041290283,0.036254883,0.0005068779,0.03491211,0.007205963,-0.006626129,0.03778076,-0.008857727,-0.01763916,0.025390625,-0.0209198,0.03375244,0.026016235,0.027679443,-0.03842163,0.03475952,-2.4080276e-05,-0.10736084,0.041412354,0.000641346,-0.011413574,-0.028045654,-0.021011353,-0.02406311,-0.015205383,0.002336502,-0.042022705,-0.034576416,-0.037750244,0.0028953552,-0.011489868,-0.028366089,-0.0043640137,0.020248413,-0.011665344,-0.011734009,-0.04333496,-0.0009975433,-0.014556885,0.013381958,-0.019104004,-0.019607544,-0.0154800415,-0.041046143,0.012374878,-0.04196167,-0.015144348,0.00868988,-0.003616333,-0.040618896,0.017410278,-0.07122803,0.0061912537,0.0054473877,-0.010292053,