INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('12681c16-de99-4205-b978-4b2e58dcd2ee', 'Software Engineer', 'Engineering', '**Job Title:** Software Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a leading tech company specializing in innovative software solutions that empower businesses and enhance user experiences. Our commitment to excellence and creativity drives us to develop cutting-edge technology that meets the diverse needs of our clients.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a talented Software Engineer to join our dynamic Engineering team. In this remote position, you will play a crucial role in designing, developing, and maintaining high-quality software applications. You will collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver exceptional products that align with our company’s vision and goals.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design, develop, and maintain scalable web applications using JavaScript, React, and Node.js.  
- Collaborate with product managers and designers to gather requirements and implement features.  
- Write clean, maintainable, and efficient code while adhering to best practices and coding standards.  
- Troubleshoot and debug applications to ensure optimal performance and user experience.  
- Participate in code reviews and provide constructive feedback to team members.  
- Stay up to date with emerging technologies and industry trends to continuously improve our software solutions.  
- Contribute to the development of technical documentation and user manuals.  
- Assist in the integration of third-party APIs and services.  
- Collaborate with QA teams to ensure high-quality deliverables.  
- Mentor junior developers and share knowledge within the team.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proficiency in JavaScript, React, and Node.js.  
- Strong understanding of web development principles and best practices.  
- Experience with version control systems, such as Git.  
- Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.  
- Ability to work independently and as part of a collaborative team.  
- Strong communication skills, both written and verbal.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with TypeScript.  
- Familiarity with GraphQL.  
- Knowledge of cloud services (e.g., AWS, Azure).  
- Understanding of Agile methodologies.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of $80,000–$100,000.  
- Flexible remote work arrangement.  
- Opportunities for professional development and career growth.  
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.  
- Access to the latest tools and technologies.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is fully remote, allowing you to work from anywhere in the UK. We value work-life balance and offer flexible working hours to accommodate your needs. 

Join us in shaping the future of technology and making a difference through innovative software solutions!', '[-0.025985718,0.016601562,0.026809692,0.04034424,0.0335083,-0.01828003,-0.024749756,0.048858643,-0.01927185,0.038238525,0.0021476746,-0.041931152,-0.01689148,-0.018539429,0.04711914,0.06213379,-0.055023193,-0.003698349,-0.014457703,-0.003255844,0.012237549,-0.005771637,0.0061149597,0.014564514,0.021240234,-0.043884277,-0.024612427,0.03967285,-0.040496826,-0.0107803345,0.01828003,-0.0062446594,-0.027069092,0.020324707,0.024658203,0.02130127,0.026535034,0.028030396,-0.009178162,0.01637268,-0.05657959,-0.06427002,0.04043579,0.029754639,-0.050628662,0.03640747,-0.049316406,0.029418945,0.03579712,-0.015556335,-0.016647339,-0.035980225,0.0067710876,0.027069092,0.011543274,-0.010917664,0.010803223,0.047332764,0.0006608963,0.008522034,0.07556152,-0.019866943,0.04711914,0.039367676,-0.008049011,0.028961182,-0.019134521,0.014770508,-0.0025253296,-0.0030517578,0.054626465,0.053253174,-0.007675171,-0.015556335,0.057891846,-0.03643799,-0.014526367,0.012145996,-0.025863647,-0.03137207,-0.082214355,0.0021533966,0.019180298,-0.035736084,-0.009170532,-0.04159546,-0.015853882,-0.08630371,-0.051452637,0.0345459,-0.044067383,0.03894043,-0.0137786865,0.028076172,0.00037622452,0.014877319,0.0057907104,0.005088806,-0.025650024,0.022720337,0.009063721,-0.04373169,-0.0017824173,0.0023212433,0.05407715,0.016540527,0.0107040405,-0.00046014786,0.05117798,-0.0004553795,-0.07891846,0.031433105,0.01398468,-0.0077781677,-0.013542175,-0.037017822,-0.039489746,-0.04083252,-0.014320374,-0.05783081,-0.044433594,-0.029586792,-0.002128601,-0.029846191,-0.0060157776,0.017318726,-0.01876831,0.0014104843,-0.050109863,-0.022979736,0.013374329,0.0079422,0.03125,-0.007965088,0.0010786057,-0.014663696,-0.07373047,0.014419556,-0.07098389,0.0035095215,-0.0024852753,-0.0184021,-0.015930176,0.0056381226,-0.025741577,-0.029190063,-0.017349243,0.029769897,-0.046051025,0.013656616,-0.005947113,0.009613037,-0.