INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('b647d1ee-18a9-40c4-8cb8-c8840a6bed40', 'Contract AI/ML Engineer', 'Engineering', '**Job Title:** Contract AI/ML Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a forward-thinking tech company dedicated to enhancing digital skills across various sectors. Our mission is to empower individuals and organisations through innovative technology solutions. We pride ourselves on fostering a diverse and inclusive workplace where every team member can thrive and contribute to our shared goals.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a Contract AI/ML Engineer to join our dynamic Engineering team. In this role, you will leverage your expertise in AI and machine learning to develop and optimise LLM-based applications and RAG architectures. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to deliver cutting-edge solutions that drive our mission forward.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design and implement AI/ML models and algorithms for LLM-based applications.
- Develop and optimise RAG architectures to enhance performance and scalability.
- Utilise Azure AI services to build and deploy machine learning solutions.
- Collaborate with software engineers and data scientists to integrate AI/ML capabilities into existing systems.
- Conduct performance optimisation techniques to ensure high efficiency and effectiveness of AI models.
- Monitor and evaluate the performance of AI systems and make necessary adjustments.
- Document processes and maintain clear communication with stakeholders throughout project lifecycles.
- Stay updated on industry trends and advancements in AI/ML technologies.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proven experience in AI/ML engineering.
- Strong knowledge of LLM-based applications and RAG architectures.
- Proficiency in Azure AI services.
- Expertise in Python programming.
- Familiarity with performance optimisation techniques.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with other cloud platforms.
- Knowledge of additional programming languages.
- Familiarity with data engineering concepts.
- Understanding of ethical AI practices.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band (to be discussed).
- Opportunity to work on innovative projects in a supportive environment.
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.
- Commitment to professional development and continuous learning.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This role is based in the UK, with flexible working arrangements available to accommodate your needs. We encourage applications from candidates across the country. 

Join us in shaping the future of digital skills and technology!', '[-0.021377563,-0.0047683716,0.024337769,0.01687622,0.0064315796,-0.027648926,-0.030273438,0.035247803,-0.019729614,0.039398193,-0.016113281,-0.06793213,-0.011390686,0.0001552105,0.008811951,0.028030396,-0.0748291,0.0071144104,0.000729084,0.01259613,0.019546509,6.389618e-05,0.0070724487,0.022262573,-0.016082764,-0.047424316,0.03173828,-0.0044898987,-0.018798828,0.010894775,0.047027588,-0.017166138,-0.051879883,0.019454956,-0.007331848,0.03756714,0.017196655,0.034454346,-0.019866943,0.0077590942,-0.017471313,-0.07446289,0.030212402,0.037597656,-0.021362305,0.03137207,-0.010307312,-0.010765076,0.024658203,0.0020828247,-0.032958984,-0.039123535,0.022583008,0.029800415,-0.0041656494,0.02142334,0.0010786057,0.027008057,0.05029297,-3.2663345e-05,0.031341553,-0.015129089,0.050079346,0.020217896,-0.018753052,0.01158905,-0.028686523,0.03579712,-0.032287598,-0.010772705,0.043151855,0.015052795,0.009002686,-0.0031375885,0.014305115,-0.040771484,-0.02607727,0.048797607,-0.028045654,-0.03579712,-0.06137085,0.014511108,0.03048706,-0.0284729,0.012054443,-0.04208374,-0.027496338,-0.055908203,-0.06689453,0.03768921,-0.04071045,0.025680542,-0.024414062,0.026031494,0.03353882,0.022384644,0.02420044,0.0036125183,-0.006175995,0.05795288,-0.005218506,-0.02861023,0.052246094,0.012588501,0.04421997,0.004020691,0.027664185,-0.039611816,0.017990112,0.023880005,-0.103271484,0.020355225,0.00059986115,0.004447937,-0.00894165,-0.012145996,-0.019088745,-0.01828003,-0.014144897,-0.06774902,-0.04714966,-0.043029785,0.006351471,-0.0132369995,-0.011184692,-0.00048708916,0.01977539,-0.034942627,-0.032592773,-0.011077881,-0.021514893,0.033996582,0.054138184,-0.028549194,-0.0023231506,-0.035247803,-0.016983032,0.014968872,-0.055145264,-0.011009216,0.03125,-0.0020999908,-0.039733887,0.064331055,-0.06640625,-0.0064353943,-0.02368164,-0.0028362274,-0.018203735,0.016693115,-0.008110046,-0.008346558,-0.047973633,-0.0020713806,0.024093628,-0.03