INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('9b2d3d34-371d-47b0-97fe-090b485be68f', 'NLP ML Engineer', 'General', '**Job Title:** NLP ML Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a forward-thinking technology company based in London, dedicated to leveraging cutting-edge artificial intelligence to drive innovation across various industries. Our team is passionate about creating impactful solutions that enhance user experiences and streamline processes. We value diversity, collaboration, and continuous learning, fostering an inclusive environment where every team member can thrive.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a talented and motivated NLP ML Engineer to join our dynamic team. In this role, you will be responsible for developing and implementing advanced natural language processing models and machine learning algorithms. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality solutions that meet our clients'' needs.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design, develop, and deploy NLP models to solve complex problems.
- Collaborate with data scientists and software engineers to integrate machine learning solutions into production systems.
- Conduct research to stay updated on the latest advancements in NLP and machine learning.
- Evaluate and optimize existing models to improve performance and accuracy.
- Prepare and preprocess text data for analysis and model training.
- Document processes and results to ensure transparency and reproducibility.
- Participate in code reviews and contribute to team knowledge sharing.
- Assist in troubleshooting and resolving issues related to NLP systems.
- Engage with stakeholders to gather requirements and provide technical insights.

**Required Skills:**  
- Strong experience in Natural Language Processing (NLP).
- Proficiency in Machine Learning techniques and frameworks.
- Solid programming skills in languages such as Python or Java.
- Familiarity with data manipulation and analysis libraries (e.g., Pandas, NumPy).
- Ability to work collaboratively in a team-oriented environment.
- Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with deep learning frameworks (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch).
- Knowledge of cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Azure) for deploying machine learning models.
- Understanding of software development best practices, including version control.
- Familiarity with data visualization tools and techniques.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £50,000.
- Opportunities for professional development and career advancement.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible work arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with options for hybrid working arrangements to accommodate your needs. 

We encourage applications from individuals of all backgrounds and experiences. If you are passionate about NLP and machine learning and are eager to contribute to innovative projects, we invite you to apply!', '[-0.027175903,0.022872925,0.035491943,-0.0060195923,0.010154724,3.6656857e-05,-0.024429321,0.07196045,-0.042175293,0.026641846,0.008102417,-0.03753662,-0.04498291,0.018188477,0.0317688,0.037200928,-0.051452637,0.0112838745,-0.0014543533,0.030334473,0.018005371,0.024795532,-0.006134033,0.029525757,0.016021729,-0.030471802,-0.012130737,0.041259766,-0.00018405914,-0.011352539,0.012245178,-0.00982666,-0.06652832,0.051208496,-0.012931824,0.011833191,0.010017395,0.032073975,-0.025604248,0.02217102,-0.01838684,-0.060699463,0.042388916,0.029708862,-0.041259766,0.030380249,-0.036865234,-0.0066490173,0.02758789,0.011444092,-0.015686035,-0.048583984,0.013183594,0.025375366,-0.0017213821,0.0107421875,0.03186035,0.016448975,-0.0009050369,-0.013031006,0.032836914,-0.03390503,0.06323242,0.034057617,-0.012763977,-0.016189575,-0.02659607,0.0016489029,-0.03616333,0.006061554,0.061035156,0.0423584,-0.027908325,0.005207062,0.0181427,-0.04550171,-0.051574707,0.039154053,-0.058898926,-0.046844482,-0.05783081,0.0018596649,0.010910034,-0.023223877,-0.021560669,-0.048217773,-0.024520874,-0.04486084,-0.06427002,0.009307861,-0.030899048,0.016403198,-0.019897461,0.054840088,0.029907227,0.01889038,0.025909424,0.011451721,-0.020233154,0.02760315,-0.025909424,-0.011917114,0.02166748,-0.007183075,0.03665161,0.013343811,0.026428223,-0.03265381,0.024780273,0.011047363,-0.09423828,0.039855957,0.005191803,-0.014228821,-0.022232056,-0.024963379,-0.009719849,-0.016815186,-0.014633179,-0.061523438,-0.042816162,-0.041809082,0.012779236,-0.030166626,-0.039794922,-0.004611969,0.023269653,-0.0014162064,-0.016067505,-0.028030396,-0.01979065,-0.0016460419,0.01977539,-0.004787445,-0.01524353,-0.033843994,-0.043518066,0.028137207,-0.046081543,-0.0013771057,0.00712204,-0.01651001,-0.040985107,0.034240723,-