INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('d4789019-b5d2-451d-9514-f60c21c29b6a', 'ML Engineer', 'General', '**Job Title:** ML Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a leading tech company specializing in AI and machine learning solutions. Our mission is to drive innovation and deliver cutting-edge technology that empowers businesses to harness the power of data. We pride ourselves on fostering a collaborative and inclusive work environment where every team member can thrive.

**The Role:**  
As an ML Engineer, you will play a crucial role in developing and implementing machine learning models that solve complex business challenges. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to translate data-driven insights into actionable strategies, contributing to the overall success of our AI initiatives.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Design, develop, and deploy machine learning models to address specific business needs.  
- Conduct data analysis and statistical modeling to extract insights from large datasets.  
- Collaborate with data scientists and software engineers to integrate ML solutions into production systems.  
- Continuously evaluate and improve model performance through rigorous testing and validation.  
- Stay up-to-date with the latest advancements in machine learning and AI technologies.  
- Document processes and maintain clear communication with stakeholders regarding project progress.  
- Assist in the development of best practices for data handling and model deployment.  
- Participate in code reviews and contribute to a culture of knowledge sharing within the team.  
- Mentor junior team members and support their professional development.  

**Required Skills:**  
- Proficiency in machine learning techniques and algorithms.  
- Strong programming skills in Python, with experience in relevant libraries (e.g., TensorFlow, Scikit-learn).  
- Solid understanding of data analysis and statistical modeling principles.  
- Experience with data preprocessing and feature engineering.  

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Familiarity with deep learning frameworks and methodologies.  
- Knowledge of natural language processing (NLP) techniques.  
- Experience with big data technologies (e.g., Hadoop, Spark).  

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £90,000.  
- Opportunities for professional growth and development.  
- A supportive and inclusive workplace culture.  
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.  

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with flexible work arrangements available to accommodate individual needs.  

We welcome applications from all qualified candidates and are committed to creating a diverse and inclusive environment. If you are passionate about machine learning and eager to make an impact, we would love to hear from you!', '[-0.010398865,0.0063819885,0.03326416,0.0064048767,0.018478394,-0.00069379807,-0.013809204,0.063964844,-0.045013428,0.022033691,0.0011749268,-0.07128906,-0.026947021,0.01676941,0.030715942,0.034606934,-0.05255127,0.0071258545,-0.009727478,0.029083252,0.024536133,0.015838623,-0.010139465,0.019561768,0.02619934,-0.029067993,-0.008041382,0.029083252,-0.0024147034,-0.013198853,0.030197144,-0.007545471,-0.08532715,0.04989624,-0.0038909912,0.018554688,0.0019035339,0.036987305,-0.02619934,0.019989014,-0.01222229,-0.06021118,0.03668213,0.034088135,-0.035217285,0.019714355,-0.019210815,-0.024230957,0.022766113,0.021224976,-0.018035889,-0.038970947,-0.008972168,0.030578613,0.015029907,0.021850586,0.022720337,0.014846802,0.0031852722,-0.007270813,0.030090332,-0.024230957,0.049743652,0.012626648,-0.00042033195,-0.03765869,-0.02078247,0.014465332,-0.02960205,-0.009521484,0.05239868,0.020019531,-0.0013008118,0.0101623535,0.028198242,-0.0446167,-0.06262207,0.041046143,-0.05328369,-0.0473938,-0.054748535,-0.012229919,0.01789856,-0.020736694,-0.017913818,-0.031402588,-0.027435303,-0.051116943,-0.051116943,0.020050049,-0.029067993,0.01828003,-0.030151367,0.06036377,0.018295288,0.031707764,0.015312195,0.0047798157,-0.026229858,0.049713135,-0.024017334,-0.029037476,0.043518066,0.004989624,0.028457642,-0.0012073517,0.012023926,-0.034729004,0.03479004,0.021453857,-0.070373535,0.025619507,0.01071167,-0.0031471252,-0.03451538,-0.015380859,-0.021820068,-0.009567261,-0.025909424,-0.07745361,-0.049865723,-0.03857422,0.012649536,-0.045837402,-0.03945923,0.014854431,0.031311035,-0.01600647,-0.026184082,-0.024093628,-0.031463623,-0.0027713776,0.009117126,-0.0034008026,0.013587952,-0.03152466,-0.050689697,0.025177002,-0.06088257,-0.012168884,0.020141602,-0.0050582886,-0.