INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('25a35eaa-ae17-41ff-a69a-a3a1a2e9622d', 'AI Engineer', 'General', '**Job Title:** AI Engineer

**About the Company:**  
We are a forward-thinking technology firm based in London, dedicated to harnessing the power of artificial intelligence to drive innovation and enhance user experiences. Our diverse team is passionate about developing cutting-edge solutions that make a real impact in various industries. We value collaboration, creativity, and a commitment to excellence.

**The Role:**  
As an AI Engineer, you will play a pivotal role in designing and implementing advanced AI models and algorithms. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to develop intelligent systems that meet the needs of our clients and contribute to our mission of delivering exceptional technology solutions.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Develop and implement machine learning and deep learning models to solve complex problems.
- Conduct data analysis to extract insights and inform decision-making processes.
- Collaborate with software engineers and data scientists to integrate AI solutions into existing systems.
- Optimize algorithms for performance and scalability.
- Stay updated on the latest advancements in AI and machine learning technologies.
- Document processes, models, and findings to ensure knowledge sharing within the team.
- Participate in code reviews and contribute to best practices in software development.
- Assist in troubleshooting and debugging AI-related issues.
- Mentor junior team members and contribute to their professional development.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proficiency in Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, and Deep Learning methodologies.
- Strong programming skills in Python.
- Experience with data analysis techniques and tools.
- Ability to work collaboratively in a team-oriented environment.
- Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Familiarity with cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Azure, Google Cloud).
- Experience with frameworks such as TensorFlow or PyTorch.
- Knowledge of natural language processing (NLP) techniques.
- Understanding of software development best practices and version control systems.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary of £90,000.
- Opportunities for professional growth and development.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with options for hybrid working arrangements to accommodate individual preferences.', '[-0.028198242,-0.0014572144,0.030303955,0.010940552,0.02293396,-0.012870789,-0.020080566,0.057281494,-0.01576233,0.017807007,-0.014183044,-0.06628418,-0.013168335,-0.008300781,0.025756836,0.047912598,-0.0703125,0.01689148,0.003742218,-0.0022125244,0.0021305084,0.020568848,-0.0043144226,0.025253296,0.016525269,-0.03302002,-0.0041542053,0.025619507,-0.0099487305,0.002960205,0.031951904,-0.014472961,-0.07086182,0.032440186,-0.01171875,0.012168884,0.0076408386,0.044158936,-0.024429321,0.01436615,0.004173279,-0.04119873,0.043823242,0.030029297,-0.046295166,0.015258789,-0.016494751,-0.009498596,0.003736496,0.0038394928,-0.016616821,-0.017486572,-0.006450653,0.030380249,-0.002626419,0.033081055,0.016921997,0.03366089,0.020980835,-0.0030765533,0.025527954,-0.014808655,0.070129395,0.03353882,-0.016326904,-0.011947632,-0.024398804,0.029815674,-0.023712158,-0.025924683,0.036315918,0.057891846,-0.004486084,0.0036125183,0.02507019,-0.044921875,-0.051879883,0.05593872,-0.040405273,-0.032196045,-0.06921387,0.010612488,0.014198303,-0.029541016,0.0041656494,-0.05545044,-0.029754639,-0.048095703,-0.06274414,0.024169922,-0.030044556,0.018859863,-0.027832031,0.029586792,0.017623901,0.0041923523,0.037353516,0.01247406,-0.02557373,0.045074463,-0.017059326,-0.02670288,0.018539429,0.030715942,0.028015137,0.010787964,0.034698486,-0.026428223,0.029632568,0.019470215,-0.08673096,0.024810791,-0.009689331,0.001950264,-0.045196533,-0.027114868,-0.020584106,-0.004497528,-0.008964539,-0.07861328,-0.03805542,-0.03375244,0.014160156,-0.007511139,-0.023956299,-0.0024700165,0.026428223,-0.035186768,-0.03125,-0.051513672,-0.021469116,0.02330017,0.014457703,-0.013549805,0.008888245,-0.060577393,-0.033599854,0.030838013,-0.05456543,-0.03201294,0.008468628,0.0016183853,-0.050872803,0.030181885,-0.055725098,0.005622864,-0.009391785,-0.00674057,-0.030715942,0.033569336,-0.007972717,0.0088