INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('d93c2c39-8944-494b-bb81-a60957b09c07', 'Universe', 'General', '**Job Title:** Research Scientist in Cosmology and Astrophysics

**About the Company:**  
We are a pioneering research organisation dedicated to exploring the depths of space and understanding the fundamental principles that govern our universe. Our team comprises leading scientists, researchers, and educators who are passionate about advancing knowledge in the fields of cosmology, astrophysics, and astronomy. We are committed to fostering an inclusive and diverse work environment where innovative ideas can flourish.

**The Role:**  
As a key member of our research team, you will contribute to groundbreaking studies in cosmology and astrophysics. Your expertise will help us unravel the mysteries of the universe, from the formation of galaxies to the fundamental laws of physics. This role offers an exciting opportunity to collaborate with a diverse group of professionals and engage in cutting-edge research.

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Conduct research in cosmology and astrophysics to advance our understanding of the universe.
- Analyse astronomical data and develop theoretical models to interpret findings.
- Collaborate with interdisciplinary teams to design and implement research projects.
- Present research findings at conferences and publish in peer-reviewed journals.
- Mentor junior researchers and contribute to their professional development.
- Stay updated on the latest developments in physics and mathematics related to cosmology.
- Participate in outreach activities to educate the public about astronomical discoveries.
- Contribute to grant writing and funding proposals to support ongoing research initiatives.

**Required Skills:**
- Strong background in cosmology, astrophysics, physics, mathematics, and astronomy.
- Proficiency in data analysis and statistical methods.
- Excellent problem-solving and critical-thinking skills.
- Strong written and verbal communication abilities.
- Ability to work collaboratively in a multidisciplinary team environment.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**
- Experience with programming languages commonly used in data analysis (e.g., Python, R).
- Familiarity with observational techniques and instrumentation in astronomy.
- Previous experience in grant writing or project management.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band (to be discussed during the interview process).
- Opportunities for professional development and continuous learning.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in [Location], with options for hybrid or remote work arrangements available. 

We welcome applications from individuals of all backgrounds and experiences. If you are passionate about exploring the universe and meet the required skills, we encourage you to apply.', '[-0.0021018982,0.026611328,0.041900635,0.03488159,0.003818512,0.0024318695,-0.039978027,0.038635254,-0.014717102,0.029434204,-0.04650879,-0.023284912,-0.030654907,-0.045959473,0.06262207,0.047180176,-0.076171875,0.05038452,0.016967773,0.05307007,0.011177063,-0.031173706,-0.00012552738,0.024139404,0.006664276,-0.093444824,-0.028015137,0.012886047,0.029525757,-0.0034065247,0.029724121,-0.016204834,-0.062347412,0.045318604,-0.034484863,0.072387695,-0.018356323,0.0023040771,-0.02645874,-0.023025513,0.0006594658,-0.059051514,0.035827637,0.013946533,-0.082214355,0.0023651123,-0.09350586,-0.01737976,0.019104004,-0.03286743,-0.0058631897,-0.02772522,0.010650635,0.0154953,-0.0066566467,-0.016525269,0.018066406,-0.0051078796,-0.0051078796,0.005760193,0.025863647,0.03262329,0.027633667,0.024612427,-0.011749268,0.024276733,0.011520386,0.036102295,-0.038116455,0.024597168,0.06958008,0.02456665,-0.0002605915,0.025741577,0.057037354,-0.06713867,-0.027389526,0.033081055,-0.04119873,-0.028762817,-0.052734375,0.023117065,0.06149292,-0.043029785,-0.007160187,-0.009101868,0.0004892349,-0.076171875,-0.06518555,0.016143799,-0.005542755,-0.0077705383,-0.030227661,0.029327393,0.021255493,-0.03753662,0.008392334,-0.023406982,0.020874023,0.027267456,0.0010948181,-0.02545166,0.014907837,-0.04324341,0.05432129,0.054656982,0.020126343,-0.02734375,0.02986145,0.002790451,-0.08660889,0.022491455,-0.0024871826,-0.008964539,-0.058807373,-0.03475952,-0.041748047,-0.043884277,-0.038909912,-0.044525146,-0.005290985,-0.02810669,0.0317688,0.015266418,0.014175415,-0.019973755,-0.0013952255,-0.032226562,-0.058776855,-0.004016876,0.006626129,-0.032958984,0.009353638,-0.021102905,-0.022201538,-0.023895264,-0.03741455,0.00037407875,-0.032226562,0.00067043304,0.040771484,-0.0011930466,0.0010795593,0.03677368,0.005065918,-0.02