INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('c890d664-458b-4c3f-839a-03e5cca3669d', 'NLP Engineer', 'General', '**Job Title:** NLP Engineer

**About the Company:**  
InvictusHiring is a forward-thinking technology firm dedicated to leveraging artificial intelligence to solve complex problems. Our team is passionate about innovation and committed to delivering cutting-edge solutions that enhance user experience and drive business success. We foster a collaborative environment where creativity and technical expertise thrive.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a talented NLP Engineer to join our dynamic team in London. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning, with a passion for developing intelligent systems that understand and generate human language. This role offers the opportunity to work on exciting projects that have a real impact on our clients and their customers.

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Design and implement NLP models and algorithms to improve language understanding and generation.
- Collaborate with data scientists and software engineers to integrate NLP solutions into existing systems.
- Conduct data analysis to identify trends and insights that inform model development.
- Optimize and fine-tune NLP models for performance and accuracy.
- Stay updated with the latest advancements in NLP and machine learning technologies.
- Participate in code reviews and contribute to best practices in software development.
- Document processes and maintain clear communication within the team and with stakeholders.
- Provide support and troubleshooting for deployed NLP solutions.

**Required Skills:**
- Proficiency in Natural Language Processing techniques and frameworks.
- Strong experience in Machine Learning algorithms and methodologies.
- Proficient in Python programming for data analysis and model development.
- Solid understanding of data analysis principles and techniques.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**
- Experience with deep learning frameworks such as TensorFlow or PyTorch.
- Familiarity with cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Google Cloud) for deploying NLP applications.
- Knowledge of additional programming languages (e.g., Java, R).
- Understanding of linguistic principles and their application in NLP.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary of £70,000.
- Opportunities for professional development and continuous learning.
- A collaborative and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with options for hybrid working arrangements to accommodate personal preferences and needs.', '[-0.04537964,0.032348633,0.054901123,-0.00023317337,0.00655365,-0.014533997,-0.033416748,0.051635742,-0.032440186,0.01234436,0.0042915344,-0.030548096,-0.027923584,-0.0066833496,0.04788208,0.037078857,-0.0440979,0.024642944,-0.035583496,0.031677246,0.0068588257,0.020828247,-0.000729084,0.041259766,0.010818481,-0.027877808,-0.013763428,0.04397583,0.011955261,-0.007167816,0.007461548,-0.019424438,-0.064819336,0.047729492,-0.0047035217,0.008605957,0.033325195,0.03387451,-0.038146973,0.023788452,-0.009338379,-0.054107666,0.028060913,0.033416748,-0.035858154,0.020690918,-0.024642944,0.009681702,-0.0018167496,-0.01424408,-0.010467529,-0.03970337,0.012489319,0.041381836,-0.0152282715,0.011451721,0.009864807,0.010795593,-0.0061416626,-0.026428223,0.010810852,-0.033416748,0.07489014,0.040618896,-0.0038852692,-0.0043182373,-0.026794434,-0.0058288574,-0.042053223,0.0006070137,0.055847168,0.07763672,-0.018753052,0.015213013,0.023086548,-0.030288696,-0.061523438,0.047058105,-0.026535034,-0.055999756,-0.054260254,-0.008705139,0.020980835,-0.03326416,-0.029510498,-0.055999756,-0.026123047,-0.039642334,-0.053894043,0.018234253,-0.026565552,0.02520752,-0.029327393,0.01586914,-0.0004968643,-0.0046806335,0.024368286,0.010467529,-0.012863159,0.032989502,-0.019439697,-0.011383057,0.009361267,-0.0069236755,0.025375366,0.020706177,0.0340271,-0.018920898,0.03591919,-0.0071525574,-0.09857178,0.03149414,0.0026416779,-0.020645142,-0.017944336,-0.03604126,-0.021652222,-0.015533447,0.004295349,-0.06213379,-0.036468506,-0.04486084,0.0004389286,-0.027297974,-0.033721924,-0.020874023,0.028015137,0.008422852,-0.012489319,-0.034484863,-0.026046753,0.015716553,0.025939941,-0.0045547485,-0.031982422,-0.037322998,-0.040496826,0.03463745,-0.04260254,0.0021762848,-0.015281677,-0.024993896,-0.039123535,0.023864746,-0.06384277,-0.015838623,0.0069236755,0.0026397705,-0.03237915,0.