INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('afb665d7-a660-4a78-990a-ea0fde236bd4', 'Product Manager', 'Product', '**Job Title: Product Manager**

**About the Company:**  
We are a fast-growing fintech startup dedicated to providing innovative financial solutions to consumers and businesses. Our mission is to revolutionise the way financial services are delivered, making them more accessible and user-friendly. Join us in shaping the future of finance!

**The Role:**  
As a Product Manager, you will play a pivotal role in driving the development and enhancement of our product offerings. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to ensure that our products meet market needs and deliver exceptional user experiences. This position is fully remote, allowing for flexibility and work-life balance.

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Define and communicate the product vision and strategy.
- Collaborate with engineering, design, and marketing teams to deliver high-quality products.
- Conduct market research to identify customer needs and market trends.
- Prioritise product features and manage the product backlog in an Agile environment.
- Analyse data and user feedback to inform product decisions and improvements.
- Develop user experience designs that enhance customer satisfaction and engagement.
- Monitor product performance and iterate based on insights and analytics.
- Facilitate stakeholder meetings to gather input and align on product direction.
- Ensure timely delivery of product milestones and objectives.
- Stay updated on industry trends and competitor activities to maintain a competitive edge.

**Required Skills:**
- Proven experience in product management within a technology-driven environment.
- Strong understanding of Agile methodologies and product development processes.
- Proficient in conducting market research and user experience design.
- Excellent data analysis skills to drive informed decision-making.
- Effective communication and collaboration skills to work with diverse teams.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**
- Experience in the fintech industry.
- Familiarity with regulatory requirements related to financial products.
- Knowledge of project management principles and practices.
- Strong stakeholder management abilities.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £60,000–£80,000, commensurate with experience.
- Opportunity to work in a dynamic and innovative environment.
- Flexible remote work arrangement.
- Professional development and growth opportunities.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is fully remote, allowing you to work from anywhere in the UK. We embrace a flexible work culture that promotes a healthy work-life balance. 

If you are passionate about product management and eager to make a significant impact in the fintech space, we would love to hear from you!', '[-0.009689331,0.021591187,0.023773193,0.032073975,-0.010604858,0.012001038,-0.02671814,0.07574463,0.029052734,0.014587402,0.02029419,-0.065979004,-0.0019893646,-0.041809082,0.039764404,0.026062012,-0.0715332,0.00043320656,-0.026168823,0.01033783,0.038024902,0.022613525,-0.0036354065,0.0030231476,0.007843018,-0.04067993,-0.04159546,0.007663727,-0.01713562,0.014633179,0.02519226,-0.007144928,-0.055603027,0.025054932,0.030227661,0.0032634735,0.000975132,0.035949707,0.006378174,0.0093307495,-0.0340271,-0.044311523,0.03741455,0.003665924,-0.011077881,0.024490356,0.013671875,0.012138367,0.017196655,0.012161255,0.0028533936,-0.05819702,0.000228405,0.044006348,0.01461792,-0.025466919,0.01777649,0.011054993,-0.005344391,0.020111084,0.046173096,-0.011390686,0.06817627,0.0043029785,-0.007648468,-0.0017642975,-0.024642944,0.021011353,-0.054229736,0.0067253113,0.02734375,0.023162842,-0.028076172,0.021713257,0.027160645,-0.0635376,-0.031677246,0.0048561096,-0.0031394958,-0.05606079,-0.06185913,-0.029403687,0.01260376,-0.01638794,0.01171875,-0.038970947,-0.015731812,-0.04458618,-0.03845215,0.051696777,-0.029083252,0.01360321,-0.051879883,0.016815186,-0.01184082,-0.002752304,-0.006336212,0.022903442,-0.028305054,0.017791748,0.0119018555,0.012878418,0.0034065247,-0.013015747,0.021148682,0.020065308,0.013381958,-0.00070667267,0.035705566,-0.00667572,-0.06762695,0.024230957,0.002855301,0.02444458,-0.048736572,-0.024230957,-0.07055664,-0.017364502,-0.017105103,-0.05508423,-0.05545044,-0.013977051,-0.0138168335,0.005996704,0.023223877,0.044952393,-0.050872803,0.0088272095,-0.060913086,-0.037322998,-0.0003285408,-0.01285553,0.019882202,-0.013931274,-0.019729614,0.002456665,-0.062469482,0.046813965,-0.057556152,-0.01977539,-0.02015686,-0.017196655,-0.013191223,-0.0030384064,-0.013969421,-0.027404785,0.0076065063,0.054534912,-0.035308838,-0.01376342