INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('c1f7a8cb-04bd-4b5f-bfb6-74e8b63b7714', 'Java Developer', 'General', 'Sure! Here’s the revised job description without the salary information:

**Job Title: Java Developer**

**About the Company:**
InvictusHiring is a leading recruitment agency dedicated to connecting talented individuals with innovative companies. We pride ourselves on understanding the unique needs of both our clients and candidates, fostering successful partnerships that drive growth and success.

**The Role:**
We are seeking a skilled Java Developer to join our dynamic team in London. The ideal candidate will have a strong foundation in core Java and experience with Spring frameworks. This role involves developing high-quality software solutions and collaborating with cross-functional teams to enhance our product offerings.

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Design, develop, and maintain robust Java applications.
- Collaborate with product managers and other developers to define software requirements.
- Implement and integrate Spring frameworks into applications.
- Troubleshoot and debug applications to ensure optimal performance.
- Participate in code reviews to maintain code quality and share knowledge.
- Stay updated with emerging technologies and industry trends.
- Contribute to the continuous improvement of development processes and methodologies.
- Assist in the deployment and maintenance of applications in production environments.
- Document development processes and technical specifications.

**Required Skills:**
- Proficiency in core Java programming.
- Experience with Spring frameworks (Spring Boot, Spring MVC, etc.).
- Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
- Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment.
- Excellent communication skills.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**
- Familiarity with RESTful APIs and microservices architecture.
- Experience with cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, etc.).
- Knowledge of database technologies (SQL, NoSQL).
- Understanding of Agile methodologies.

**What We Offer:**
- Opportunities for professional development and career advancement.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible working arrangements.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**
- Based in London, with options for hybrid work arrangements. 

If you are passionate about software development and eager to make an impact, we would love to hear from you!', '[-0.060302734,0.02772522,0.061706543,0.006454468,0.02154541,-0.011558533,-0.039245605,0.028671265,0.016204834,0.016525269,0.03189087,-0.074523926,-0.000998497,0.024520874,0.04232788,0.036468506,-0.031982422,-0.006095886,-0.055725098,0.02180481,-0.008041382,-0.0028896332,-0.0040512085,0.03036499,0.007080078,-0.02960205,-0.05606079,0.011459351,0.022369385,0.00044107437,0.03050232,-0.012374878,-0.04119873,0.03967285,0.0073928833,-0.0005187988,0.015159607,0.045562744,0.008613586,-0.015625,-0.026885986,-0.051483154,0.040100098,0.010063171,-0.019882202,0.04724121,-0.021743774,0.0082092285,-0.019577026,-0.021636963,-0.022109985,-0.043792725,0.058044434,0.049072266,0.0010690689,-0.04788208,-0.0023994446,0.058563232,0.015136719,0.007511139,0.040740967,-0.012313843,0.02520752,0.019088745,-0.042266846,0.008354187,0.014472961,-0.024978638,-0.025650024,0.0101623535,0.05529785,0.059143066,-0.0071144104,0.020965576,0.02267456,-0.057617188,-0.009124756,0.021774292,-0.040283203,-0.01209259,-0.09338379,0.0067443848,0.044647217,-0.014282227,-0.016021729,-0.0079956055,-0.025741577,-0.045959473,-0.037719727,0.027008057,-0.030883789,0.051208496,0.011108398,0.023254395,1.5497208e-05,-0.021133423,-0.04711914,0.05130005,-0.022735596,0.035095215,0.01927185,-0.0118637085,0.0056419373,-0.03677368,0.036468506,0.007881165,0.007007599,-0.046539307,0.01739502,-0.008422852,-0.10491943,0.019973755,0.0061187744,-0.025863647,-0.021087646,-0.012420654,-0.027862549,-0.040802002,-0.035705566,-0.04473877,-0.026397705,-0.05331421,-0.009483337,-0.024032593,-0.01499939,-0.008033752,0.007369995,0.0012636185,-0.035491943,-0.01651001,0.013328552,0.008476257,0.023529053,-0.009178162,-0.033050537,-0.036865234,-0.049926758,0.041107178,-0.046844482,-0.03314209,0.0034236908,0.0042686462,-0.061584473,-0.0007047653,-0.025863647,-0.025604248,-0.002521515,-0.013061523,-0.033721924,0.015029907,-0.00047802925,0