INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('77b175e4-16f9-4dd0-9111-3324f7f8ac42', 'Engineering Program Manager', 'General', '**Job Title: Engineering Program Manager**

**About the Company:**  
InvictusHiring is a forward-thinking recruitment agency committed to connecting talented professionals with innovative companies. We pride ourselves on fostering an inclusive workplace culture and supporting our clients in building diverse teams that drive success.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking an experienced Engineering Program Manager to lead cross-functional teams in delivering complex engineering projects on time and within budget. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in project management and engineering, with the ability to communicate effectively across various stakeholders.

**Key Responsibilities:**
- Lead and manage engineering programs from inception to completion, ensuring alignment with business objectives.
- Coordinate cross-functional teams, including engineering, product management, and operations, to ensure project milestones are met.
- Develop and maintain project schedules, budgets, and resource allocation plans.
- Identify and mitigate risks throughout the project lifecycle.
- Facilitate regular project meetings and provide updates to senior management and stakeholders.
- Implement best practices in project management and engineering processes.
- Monitor project performance and prepare reports for stakeholders.
- Foster a collaborative team environment and encourage continuous improvement.
- Ensure compliance with industry standards and regulations.
- Serve as a point of contact for external partners and clients regarding project status.

**Required Skills:**
- Proven experience as a Program Manager or similar role in an engineering environment.
- Strong understanding of project management methodologies (e.g., Agile, Waterfall).
- Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.
- Ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously and meet tight deadlines.
- Proficiency in project management software and tools.
- Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**
- Experience in a specific engineering discipline (e.g., software, mechanical, electrical).
- Familiarity with Lean and Six Sigma methodologies.
- Previous experience in a leadership role.
- Knowledge of budget management and financial forecasting.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £90,000–£120,000, commensurate with experience.
- Opportunities for professional development and career advancement.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible work arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is fully remote, allowing you to work from anywhere while collaborating with a diverse team.

If you are passionate about engineering and project management and are looking to make a significant impact, we encourage you to apply!', '[-0.016082764,0.029586792,0.041015625,0.02671814,0.012817383,0.018234253,-0.030212402,0.026031494,-0.034606934,0.009712219,0.019622803,-0.06561279,-0.004840851,-0.017944336,0.08532715,0.042877197,-0.05657959,-0.0034103394,-0.03930664,0.016418457,0.027023315,0.028274536,0.017166138,0.04309082,0.0026721954,-0.024337769,-0.035949707,0.033294678,-4.8696995e-05,0.014770508,0.023208618,-0.010848999,-0.07208252,0.006000519,0.009719849,0.033233643,0.043823242,0.035949707,-0.03366089,0.04724121,0.010620117,-0.036590576,0.020065308,0.023529053,-0.020248413,0.02923584,-0.01939392,0.017501831,0.04046631,0.014656067,0.027389526,-0.034057617,0.037200928,0.031219482,0.04510498,0.010055542,0.009803772,-0.00063610077,-0.037078857,-0.027145386,0.014923096,-0.0048713684,0.061523438,0.022338867,0.0043525696,0.029769897,-0.013000488,0.021255493,-0.006362915,-0.0118255615,0.02029419,0.055603027,-0.020141602,0.024414062,0.04840088,-0.07287598,-0.048217773,0.033081055,-0.030517578,-0.026351929,-0.054779053,-0.027664185,0.019180298,-0.037750244,-0.056671143,-0.009605408,-0.042114258,-0.07305908,-0.033233643,0.02519226,-0.049346924,0.064086914,-0.028320312,0.00730896,-0.013290405,0.0015964508,0.013450623,0.02760315,0.010726929,0.050109863,0.004798889,-0.018875122,0.015380859,-0.015655518,0.024856567,0.022064209,0.018356323,-0.0007824898,0.05114746,-0.024093628,-0.06222534,0.019622803,0.013069153,0.024597168,-0.0362854,-0.016967773,-0.035980225,-0.03652954,0.0061454773,-0.051971436,-0.022918701,-0.03237915,-0.039764404,-0.022491455,0.005455017,0.021575928,-0.010238647,0.023101807,-0.032806396,-0.03756714,-0.04449463,0.016647339,0.04736328,-0.032440186,-0.021987915,-0.034820557,-0.030654907,0.031555176,-0.05307007,0.00062417984,0.0019083023,-0.014450073,-0.03173828,0.0066566467,0.001627922,-0.038970947,-0.007904053,0.009864807,0.007205963,0.0066871643,-0.00