INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('5af55850-6717-40b3-b0fc-834769b46401', 'TPM', 'General', '**Job Title:** Technical Program Manager (TPM)  

**About the Company:**  
InvictusHiring is a forward-thinking recruitment agency dedicated to connecting top talent with innovative companies. We pride ourselves on fostering a diverse and inclusive workplace, where every individual can thrive and contribute to our mission of excellence in recruitment.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a skilled Technical Program Manager (TPM) to join our dynamic team in London. The successful candidate will play a crucial role in managing and delivering complex technical projects, ensuring alignment between stakeholders and driving efficiency across teams. 

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Lead the planning and execution of technical programs from inception to completion.
- Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define project scope, goals, and deliverables.
- Monitor project progress, identify risks, and implement mitigation strategies.
- Facilitate communication between technical teams and non-technical stakeholders.
- Prepare and present project updates to senior management and key stakeholders.
- Ensure adherence to project timelines and budgets.
- Drive continuous improvement by identifying process enhancements.
- Foster a culture of collaboration and accountability within project teams.
- Manage project documentation and reporting to ensure transparency.
- Support the development of best practices in project management.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proven experience as a Technical Program Manager or similar role.
- Strong understanding of software development processes and methodologies.
- Excellent organisational and multitasking skills.
- Exceptional communication and interpersonal abilities.
- Proficiency in project management tools and software.
- Ability to work effectively in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Experience with Agile methodologies.
- Familiarity with cloud technologies and platforms.
- Knowledge of data analysis and reporting tools.
- Previous experience in a recruitment or HR-related environment.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band of £101,000.
- Opportunities for professional development and growth.
- A supportive and inclusive work environment.
- Flexible working arrangements to promote work-life balance.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in London, with flexible work arrangements available to accommodate individual needs. 

If you are passionate about driving technical projects and want to be part of a collaborative team, we encourage you to apply!', '[-0.04522705,0.035095215,0.06378174,0.016036987,-0.0073928833,-0.014549255,-0.03250122,0.037872314,-0.009414673,-0.000767231,0.020599365,-0.023666382,-0.012191772,-0.033203125,0.07458496,0.050872803,-0.049041748,-0.005947113,-0.030181885,0.036346436,0.009590149,0.023544312,-0.009384155,0.030059814,0.0063056946,-0.03692627,-0.03869629,0.03036499,0.00018107891,0.0041885376,0.06124878,-0.018203735,-0.047332764,0.023071289,0.01928711,0.0059776306,0.020431519,0.070251465,-0.010070801,0.038330078,-0.010734558,-0.0069618225,0.03488159,0.039733887,-0.0073165894,0.002544403,-0.014167786,0.015235901,0.00024843216,-0.012611389,0.036071777,-0.040374756,0.008728027,0.0736084,0.016052246,-0.006462097,-0.0067863464,0.013450623,-0.005168915,-0.025802612,0.044433594,0.0009937286,0.048065186,0.019332886,0.001455307,0.018066406,4.2557716e-05,-0.0033550262,-0.029129028,-0.0047721863,0.018920898,0.06298828,-0.013793945,0.028167725,0.061340332,-0.048431396,-0.047546387,0.048675537,-0.017150879,-0.035186768,-0.04473877,-0.032196045,0.03378296,-0.030029297,-0.035583496,-0.0014820099,-0.0418396,-0.0390625,-0.016342163,0.043426514,-0.055389404,0.06286621,-0.027511597,0.05404663,-0.013031006,-0.031219482,-0.008415222,0.011558533,-0.006126404,0.06939697,-0.0048332214,0.001958847,-0.026992798,0.0042381287,0.031311035,0.021438599,0.019714355,-0.021331787,0.05319214,-0.022079468,-0.10650635,0.011077881,-0.018692017,0.01486969,-0.011024475,-0.02684021,-0.005355835,-0.016098022,0.010292053,-0.059051514,-0.0037250519,-0.015914917,-0.04144287,-0.049713135,-0.015113831,0.0026016235,-0.012130737,-0.0033302307,-0.009689331,-0.037384033,-0.021377563,0.009414673,0.036315918,-0.01878357,0.008560181,-0.039886475,-0.050109863,0.034484863,-0.048706055,-0.00667572,-0.010948181,-0.013664246,-0.045318604,0.03918457,-0.022766113,-0.030410767,0.008399963,0.009468079,-0.042755127,0.02030