INSERT INTO public.past_jds (id, title, department, content, embedding, created_at) VALUES ('37edfb6f-08bf-4d33-96cc-7027bdbb0347', 'Graduate AI Data Scientist', 'General', '**Job Title: Graduate AI Data Scientist**

**About the Company:**  
A leading tech company focused on innovative AI solutions, we are dedicated to pushing the boundaries of technology to create impactful products and services. Our team thrives on collaboration, creativity, and a commitment to excellence.

**The Role:**  
We are seeking a Graduate AI Data Scientist to join our dynamic team. This entry-level position is ideal for recent graduates who are passionate about artificial intelligence and data science. You will work alongside experienced professionals to develop and implement AI-driven solutions that address real-world challenges.

**Key Responsibilities:**  
- Assist in the development and implementation of machine learning models.
- Conduct data analysis to derive actionable insights from large datasets.
- Utilize Python for data manipulation and analysis tasks.
- Perform statistical analysis to validate model performance and accuracy.
- Create data visualizations to communicate findings effectively.
- Collaborate with cross-functional teams to understand project requirements and objectives.
- Participate in research to explore new AI technologies and methodologies.
- Document processes and maintain clear records of work conducted.
- Contribute to team meetings and share insights on project progress.

**Required Skills:**  
- Proficiency in machine learning techniques and algorithms.
- Strong data analysis skills with experience in handling large datasets.
- Excellent programming skills in Python.
- Solid understanding of statistical analysis principles.
- Ability to create compelling data visualizations.

**Nice-to-Have Skills:**  
- Familiarity with deep learning frameworks and techniques.
- Knowledge of natural language processing (NLP) concepts.
- Experience with big data technologies and tools.

**What We Offer:**  
- Competitive salary band: £25,000 - £30,000 per annum.
- Opportunities for professional development and growth.
- A collaborative and inclusive work environment.
- Access to the latest tools and technologies in AI.

**Location & Work Arrangement:**  
This position is based in [Location] with flexible work arrangements available, including options for remote work. 

If you are ready to kickstart your career in AI and data science, we encourage you to apply and become part of our innovative team!', '[-0.018295288,0.04360962,0.033477783,0.0050468445,0.02394104,-0.028778076,-0.023391724,0.06085205,-0.022033691,0.02319336,0.0059165955,-0.049804688,-0.03555298,-0.006755829,0.029006958,0.02859497,-0.08154297,0.047302246,-0.0034160614,0.03274536,0.027252197,0.013923645,-0.0072288513,0.007385254,0.029037476,-0.056671143,0.014564514,0.032440186,-0.00907135,0.01687622,0.039215088,-0.010787964,-0.047851562,0.008743286,-0.0037899017,0.02508545,-0.0042877197,0.049346924,-0.00919342,-0.006038666,0.011016846,-0.033935547,0.03829956,0.025497437,-0.041748047,0.013938904,-0.021850586,-0.041229248,0.012557983,0.004611969,-0.042541504,-0.044158936,0.014297485,0.030960083,-0.011627197,-3.2901764e-05,0.0074920654,0.009490967,0.013687134,-0.03262329,0.046417236,0.014221191,0.060913086,0.030593872,-0.0073623657,-0.0011644363,0.010246277,0.04095459,-0.030776978,-0.0055656433,0.057739258,0.030700684,0.0029449463,0.007648468,0.016662598,-0.048980713,-0.072387695,0.01663208,-0.04824829,-0.040008545,-0.066589355,-0.004135132,0.005039215,-0.024932861,0.002714157,-0.057250977,-0.020248413,-0.06896973,-0.06829834,0.043426514,-0.02456665,0.007972717,-0.016189575,0.020523071,0.020980835,0.0069847107,0.0181427,-0.022140503,-0.012359619,0.00970459,-0.056488037,-0.033569336,0.022537231,0.032287598,0.046966553,0.0087890625,-0.0015497208,-0.011947632,0.018997192,0.032562256,-0.07788086,0.03414917,0.018722534,-0.008407593,-0.03692627,-0.021621704,-0.033203125,-0.03564453,-0.0070381165,-0.066589355,-0.03125,-0.0061416626,0.005622864,-0.002286911,-0.013008118,0.027008057,0.025253296,-0.04815674,-0.04272461,-0.03933716,-0.0056533813,0.026412964,0.038909912,-0.019592285,0.00970459,-0.049621582,-0.05593872,0.038116455,-0.05053711,-0.033294678,-0.0016832352,0.0049972534,-0.025482178,0.030426025,-0.044311523,-0.007751465,-0.00856781,0.01637268,-0.016967773,0.022964478,-0.00